                        </span></div><div class="util-bar-flyout util-bar-flyout-comments"><div class="util-bar-flyout-heading util-bar-flyout-heading-comments"><h6 class="util-bar-flyout-title util-bar-flyout-title-comments">Join the Conversation</h6><p class="util-bar-flyout-subtitle util-bar-flyout-subtitle-comments">To find out more about Facebook commenting please read the <a href="http://static.freep.com/conversation-guidelines/">Conversation Guidelines and FAQs</a></p></div><div class="util-bar-comments-wrap"><div class="util-bar-scroll-wrap util-bar-scroll-wrap-comments  "><div class="facebook-comments-plugin-wrap scrollable-content"><div class="fb-comments" data-href="http://www.freep.com/story/opinion/contributors/2015/02/06/bus-transit-metro-detroit/23016033/" data-posts="20" data-width="400"></div></div></div></div><div class="util-bar-flyout-close-ribbon"></div></div></div></div><div class="util-bar-secondary-modules"><div class="util-bar-module util-bar-module-print"><div
                        class="util-bar-btn util-bar-btn-print"
