                        By Bill Laitner
                    </div></li><li class="series-promo-item"><a class="series-promo-thumb-link" href="/story/news/local/michigan/2015/02/19/walking-man-james-robertson-detroit/23641867/"   ><img src="http://www.gannett-cdn.com/-mm-/12a0400e5f52ea1aabc744c102891f35fc27800a/c=631-0-2355-1724&amp;r=x83&amp;c=80x80/local/-/media/2015/02/18/DetroitFreePress/DetroitFreePress/635598807892116654-021815-james-robertson-vistis-class-15.jpg" width="80" height="80" alt="Norman R. Bernard Elementary School students Dilayia Dickerson and Lucas Oliveria look as principal Melanie Morey points to the Spirit of Detroit pin recently awarded to James Robertson by Detroit City Council." class="series-promo-thumb"/></a><h6 class="series-promo-headline"><a class="series-promo-headline-link" href="/story/news/local/michigan/2015/02/19/walking-man-james-robertson-detroit/23641867/"    data-ht="series2">Kids write letters to Detroit&#39;s hard-walkin&#39; worker</a></h6></li><li class="series-promo-item"><a class="series-promo-thumb-link" href="/story/news/local/michigan/oakland/2015/01/31/detroit-commuting-troy-rochester-hills-smart-ddot-ubs-banker-woodward-buses-transit/22660785/"   ><img src="http://www.gannett-cdn.com/-mm-/96409ac8792ff4cb98ca2dd977da6ed661dcc20c/c=411-0-2064-1653&amp;r=x83&amp;c=80x80/local/-/media/2015/01/31/DetroitFreePress/DetroitFreePress/635583252081774424-012915-james-the-walker-rg-11.jpg" width="80" height="80" alt="The daily route of &quot;the incredible commuter&quot; James Robertson, 56, of Detroit." class="series-promo-thumb"/><div class="play-btn-m series-promo-play-btn"></div></a><h6 class="series-promo-headline"><a class="series-promo-headline-link" href="/story/news/local/michigan/oakland/2015/01/31/detroit-commuting-troy-rochester-hills-smart-ddot-ubs-banker-woodward-buses-transit/22660785/"    data-ht="series3">Heart and sole: Detroiter walks 21 miles in work commute</a></h6><div class="series-promo-meta">
